                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Revision of the Lustre Compilation/Installation instructions to provide up to date information. - Subtask to focus only on the build/install part.&lt;br/&gt;
This is designed to expand specifics of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-539&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-539&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Locations of Lustre Build instructions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.whamcloud.com/display/PUB/Building+Lustre+from+Source&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://wiki.whamcloud.com/display/PUB/Building+Lustre+from+Source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
